Package: ldat2
Type: Package
Title: Large Data Files in R
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2015-09-10
Author: Jan van der Laan
Maintainer: Jan van der Laan <djvanderlaan@unrealizedtime.nl>
Description: Tools for handling data sets that are too large to keep in memory.
  Maps R objects to data that is kept (partially) on disk. The user kan
  interact largely with these object as he would with regular data.framas and
  vectors. 
URL: https://github.com/djvanderlaan/ldat2
Imports:
    lazyeval
Depends:
    stats,
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
